name: Jolie Anderson
description: I’m an easy-going and lively girl. My life is rather active and I’m not the one who likes to spend the most part of the tome indoors. Of course sometimes it’s great to make myself comfortable in the armchair and to read a book or to watch your favorite movie. I think that I’m sociable and open to everything new. And of course I’m very caring, loving and passionate young woman and I will be really good wife for the best man in the world!
